Name: New Campus Language Institute
Services Offered: PTE Coaching , Spoken English Classes , IELTS Coaching , TOEFL Coaching ,
Details: Apart from preparing for the D-day and aiming to score a high band, what is equally crucial, is the selection of the right Institute that gives you a platform to materialize your plans. Following are just some of the reasons why you should join US.Intelligent Learning: We define a very narrow syllabus band beyond which we guarantee will not come in the exam. The idea is to spend time ONLY on the relevant course.Finest Instructors: We adhere to the globally accepted standards of teaching. Prior to the actual classroom teaching, our trainers undergo sessions of SIMULATING TEACHING, enabling them to understand various methods and techniques that can be used to cater to individual needs of students.Updated Curriculum: The latest questions appearing in the exam are tracked and discussed in class. Effort is made to update the study material after every exam. Thus the curriculum taught is based on the latest exam pattern.Personal Assistance: When our students find themselves stuck in particular questions, they do not have to wait until their next class to get help  personal assistance from the faculty is available on a one-to-one basis.Student Module: We at New campus provide students practice material of their own. The student module contains sentence structure and vocabulary exercises to help brush up English before the actual IELTS teaching takes place. The module is self sufficient, besides the teachers' assistance, in providing students ample solved answers and exercises for further practice.Library and Resource Centre: Mega mind has the most comprehensive onsite-library for IELTS training in Surat. Efforts have been made to procure all possible books on the subject.Flexible Timings: For certain batches the classes are held every day, so the student can attend any of the one session depending on the time that suits him/her on that day.Special Taped Sessions: We audio tape student's speaking sessions for better and effective feedback. It also allows the student self evaluation and thus faster and further improvement.

Details: Welcome to TIME Triumphant Institute of Management Education Pvt. Ltd. (T.I.M.E.) is India's leading test-prep institute with a pan-India presence and is headquartered at Hyderabad. Established in 1992, T.I.M.E. today operates out of 236 offices located in 112 towns and cities across the country. Over 40 IIT/IIM graduates form part of the core team at T.I.M.E..Started in a small room of 120 square feet on 26th May,1992 in Hyderabad with one centre,  T.I.M.E. has just completed 24 years of service to the student community  helping to build a few hundred thousand careers along the way. From one office to 236 offices has been a long and satisfying journey for T.I.M.E.'s promoters who had chucked their high flying corporate jobs to pursue their dream and passion!  T.I.M.E. is today acknowledged as a multi-location, multi-programme training specialist run on corporate lines and offers a wide range of programmes not only for national and state-level entrance exams like the CAT, MAT, JEE MAIN and JEE ADVANCED, but also for international exams like GMAT, GRE, IELTS and TOEFL.

Details: Honble DirectorMr. R.K Jain the founder DIRECTOR of the NATIONAL CLASSES has been a professional academician since more than four decade{40 years}. He has been teaching ,rather mentoring the aspirants for the countrys most prestigious examinations like Civil services Examinations (for IAS, IPS, Allied Services, etc.) and the aspirants for the examinations like JEE (Main and Advance),,VITEEE, BITSAT, NATA, KCET, MCET,JKCET, COMEDK, GUJ-CET,AIIMS, AIPMT, AFMC,BHU, CMC etc ,He has enriched his academic by working in various prominent cities of India, and variety of students belonging to the different socio-academic strata.Our courses cater to all the needs of the aspirants to help them to excel in various competitive as well as Board examinations. Innovative strategies and techniques adopted in our centres, keep our students abreast of the ever-changing pattern of top level Engineering/Medical Entrance Exams.As a result NATIONALs time-tested learning formulae are percolation to far-flung areas of India to benefit students from all backgrounds.Our Future Vision:         Growth through excellence: Our Goal is to empower you to fulfill your DreamsWhy national? [Reasons to choose National]1.       Highly Qualified, Trained and Subject specialist Teachers as the real Torchbearers From top universities/ Institutes like IITs, NIITs, NSITs, Kota, Delhi and from other reputed Engineering colleges and medical colleges.2.     Conscientious Selection of faculty: We conduct campus recruitment for teachers. Each and every candidate for teaching is selected through a Conscientious process.3.     Proven Results in Entrance Exams: national has been consistently producing Rankers for two decades in most of the toughest Entrance Exams of the country like, IIT-JEE,VITEEE, BITSAT, NATA, KCET, MCET,JKCET, COMEDK, GUJ-CET,AIIMS, AIPMT, AFMC,BHU, CMC etc.4.     Integrated Teaching Methodology: We Prepare the students for competitive as well as School / Board Exams with equal focus on both simultaneously. This well-tested approach of teaching has borne splendid outcomes.5.     Exhaustive, Compact & Original Study material with SHORT CUT SOLVING techniques are designed on the latest pattern of exams by National6.     Special TARGET STUDY: We have regular and weekend batches for students studying in our academy. Out of these batches, we shortlist the students to form the target batches for their rank enhancement. It is a normal pace batch wherein students are given additional academic inputs in additional classes, simultaneously in continuation with their studies in their respective batches.7.     Special GROOMING STUDY: In this batch, we select those students whose performance is relatively low and unable to cope with school as well as competitive exams preparation. Thus, additional time is given to make them understand the Concepts, Definitions and Formulas (CDF), so that they remain motivated for their preparations & gain confidence to face the competition. This will also put an end to the need of extra tuition requirements.8.     Revision Classes: These classes serve as catalyst for weak, non-serious and shy students. During these classes, sufficient time is provided to the students for revision, and for raising doubts they are encountered with during their studies. This special session boosts the confidence and enhances the knowledge quotient of even average students parallel to that of toppers, and also motivates them to perform like the toppers.9.     Special Doubt Clearing Cell: This is a platform to provide an opportunity to students to get their doubts for all three subjects. A special team of faculties available on all working days between specified timings to clear the students academic doubts.10.  Backup Classes: "If a student misses out certain chapter or a particular class, we provide him/her the opportunity to attend the Backup class with video lecture of the same so that he/she may ride parallel to others.11.  Brilliant Initiative like Online Tests, attendance reporting and test score reporting through SMS, E-mail & Courier etc. Audio-Video classes are also conducted for better clarity of students.12.  CPTs Every Month: There will be two types of CPTs based on the different patterns and criterias as mentioned below:         JEE pattern based Test: CPTs to be held every week of the month will be based on JEE pattern of the respective topics considered in the particular week for the test.         board pattern based Test: JEE council has planned to give due weightage to board. Thus, to equip the students with necessary practice for good score in board, test will be conducted based on  board pattern in between of CPTs.13. Special Sessions:         Motivational Seminars: by experts to optimize the potential and minimize academic stress.         Mind Power Sessions: by Mind Power experts to enhance performance and success ratio.         Memory Power Sessions: by Memory Power Experts to help learn with fun & use it for success         Holistic & all inclusive Academic system: Care to all from average to brilliant, poor to rich.

Details: Swec Education & Immigration Services has been established in 2004, and it is based at C.G. Road, the heart of Ahmedabad (Gujarat), Manchester of India. We are a company having concept of giving career consultancy, dedicated for extending services to the students and people wishing to visit foreign countries.We have been successful enough in establishing our name and fame not only across Ahmedabad, but also across various locations in Gujarat and UK. We, at Swec Education & Immigration Services, believe in customized and extensive services to our clients. This is possible because of excellent knowledge and our collaborations with various Universities across the foreign countries. We have a dedicated and hardworking team to give the best solution to our client's. We have earned the trust and support of our clients, and above all, we believe in maintaining a strong, ethical and reliable team to support our activities all time.At Swec Education & Immigration Services, we provide guidance to students for their higher education, courses, countries and universities to be chosen from a wide selection. This is how we maximize the possibilities of students choosing the right path and hence the most promising career ahead. We have established ourselves as one of the most relied upon, education and immigration consultant in the region. This is a result of honest counseling to the students, expert visa advice and support. We are not only consultant for education, but also for all types of Visas including Immigration (PR), HSW, Visitor Visa, etc. Besides, we also provide other various services like Air Ticket, Bank Account Opening, Insurance and Money Exchange and providing guidance for Foreign Going Competency Exams.We are an organization providing solutions to the aspirants according to their individual requirements. In other words, we provide tailor-made solutions; this is possible because of our personalized approach to understand the financial, educational or personal profiles of the scholars. We arguably play an important role in assisting and advising the students for their career path by analyzing their qualification, abilities, skills and experience. We are proud to say that we have been doing a noble job by helping the students in designing their careers. Now Swec Education & Immigration Services is into Tours & Travels. Contact us for further details.
